Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:05.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}でも　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:13.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}止まることができなくて嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:22.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:27.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:33.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:38.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:50.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心も　未来も　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:57.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:00.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:05.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:08.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:10.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:14.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:18.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see what I want tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:28.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠と 儚さと 震える夜もあるけれど
