Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:05.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}实在过于喜欢 同时伴随些许痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:13.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}由于无法停止已经开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:22.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:33.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:38.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:50.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论心意 未来还是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:57.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}对 还有素未谋面的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:10.65,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:28.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然会有永恒和如烟以及孤单的夜晚
